messages.text: Do you see the target in the red dress?
Yes, in the park
You aren’t going to back out on me are you?
No
Who is this woman anyway?
I’ll do the rundown when you’re back at headquarters, but she’s a filthy liar
Remember this is how you prove yourself today
Just flash her the gun, and say what we rehearsed.
Also, you aren’t just getting the briefcase
What do you mean??
In your side pocket, there is a syringe.
What!?!? WITH WHAT!?
Don’t’ worry about it, just inject her with it
No, I can’t do that. Not without knowing what it is
It’s just a sedative
What for?
So she might look like she’s taking a nap, while you take the briefcase
We don’t want to draw attention here
You better not be lying to me
I don’t want to cause anyone any physical harm
That’s not what I’m about
I’m not lying!  And time is ticking
We can’t let her pass the briefcase off, we’ll be screwed
Wait. Did she used to be one of us?
She’s Damian’s ex-girlfriend. She’s trying to rat us out
How do you know she doesn’t have more copies of what’s in her briefcase
We already hacked into her computer, it’s not there.
I’m not feeling comfortable about the syringe
You have to do it.
I actually don’t have to do anything
Actually, you owe us for blowing the last operation.
That was a mistake.
A big mistake. One that could get you in jail.
You’d report me???
We saved your life if you’ve forgotten, you owe us
Any more objections
No.
Just flash the gun. Use the syringe. Get the briefcase. DO IT NOW
I’m ten feet away. Are you sure she’s alone??
Yes. Go!
Did you do it??
LAYLA??
WTF!!! ABOUT TEN COPS STARTED CHASING AFTER ME. DID YOU ALREADY FUCKING REPORT ME??
WHY WOULD I DO THAT!?!
Then how were so many there already???
I don’t know, where are you now??
I’m not fucking telling you!!
Come on, Layla
Did you get the briefcase??
Yes. But I might go throw it in the river
NO! Listen, tell me where you are, so we can send one of the vans to get you
How do I know that’s not a setup??
It’s not a setup!
How about you tell me where to send the van and you can walk toward it yourself
Layla?
I don’t know.
Why would I report you, if you were carrying out my directions
I don’t know. You tell me
You just have to trust me on this one.
I don’t. I don’t trust you at all
Come on, where are you?
How do I know you just won’t send the cops there
There will be no cops, I promise
I want Damian to be the one driving the van
Damian doesn’t drive the van
He will today. He’s the only person I trust here
Fine
If I see it’s not him, I’m throwing it in the river
Where do you want the van?
Anchorage and Bolinger.
Look out for it in 20 minutes. Keep me updated.
I see it coming
And Damian is driving.
Yes. I see that.
See? Trust.
Thank you.
They’ll slide the side door open, you just jump in
Okay.
I feel like something’s off.
It’s just the adrenaline talking
I’m walking toward it now.
Let me know when you’re inside
I’m in.
Great.  Now I’d like to apologize for what we’re about to do to you
What do you mean?
ARE YOU KIDDING ME??
THEY JUST TOOK THE BRIEFASE OUT OF MY HAND AND PUSHED ME OUT!!!
WHY???
Sorry, we need to divert the cop’s attention to carry out something else
That’s been the plan the whole time
Since you’ve been sloppy in the past, we thought you’d make a good sacrifice
CARRY OUT WHAT?
Oh my God, I’m surrounded!!
Sorry, Layla
